TransactionManager ..> ACIDWorkflow : enforces
TicketingSystem ..> TransactionManager : begin/commit
MaintenanceSchedule ..> TransactionManager : transactional updates
IncidentReport ..> TransactionManager
DataAnalyticsPlatform ..> OutboxRelay : publishes events

